{"tid":2101311,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【有感而發】有冇人想走唔係因為政治原因，而係覺得喺香港打工冇希望","createTime":"2020-07-09T16:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T04:52:16.000Z","uid":87511,"like":74,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"34411e525f7bf8dbe2eac309db4bd757f5e4f2d0","tid":2101311,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"而家做緊份閪工，日日OT半粒鐘至一粒鐘係基本，有感而發想開呢個post<br />\n<br />\n8大畢業，冇專業技能，得個讀U時考到嘅濕鳩救生員牌<br />\nGrad咗兩年仲係未到20K，返親都係濕鳩腦細濕鳩工<br />\n搞唔撚掂"},{"pid":"74ed9e1ea1f0564509cdba7df265356199f32830","tid":2101311,"uid":252142,"like":7,"dislike":44,"score":-37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:27:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5ddfec02b3a43ec4f399e33114745bf2d81fd05","tid":2101311,"uid":353836,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:29:04.000Z","msg":"香港打工叫易上位<br />\n移民咪仲死"},{"pid":"9df8cf33a0581d71fcdf54f38a8ddeeaaeef6b40","tid":2101311,"uid":87511,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:32:39.000Z","msg":"唉，講多少少我背景<br />\n<br />\n幾年前DSE差幾分先入到Ｕ，好彩最後走後門入到某U傳理科；<br />\n點解話係好彩？<br />\n因為我真係想做記者<br />\n雖然人工未必話好高，但係我相信嗰份使命感會帶到心靈上嘅滿足畀我<br />\n<br />\n咁我兩年前畢業，點知Send親CV去記者post都冇回音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自問GPA正常 (過3)，人工開得算合理，11-13K都開過<br />\n但係真係連Email覆都唔覆我&hellip;&hellip;更加係未試過見工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後一畢業就做份濕鳩in house Marketing工，日日唔知做乜鳩<br />\n做咗半年無撚端端要我跑數做sell屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撞啱上年同好多同事罷完工個支那藉腦細 (所謂港漂) 又有不滿 ，索鳩性裸辭唔撚柒做 (不過佢又有留我喎, 同埋寫畀我封reference letter都算正常同得體)<br />\n<br />\n好彩有份救生員炒散返下，撞啱武肺前嘅夏天人工係唔錯嘅，<br />\n不過唔會有前途，只能夠一路返炒散一路搵工，<br />\n然後無論係文員仔/Marketing/記者 post 我都照send CV，都係冇回音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來做某一間黃店，點知間黃店係冇管理層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係就係唔太辛苦，但係結果就係行政混亂、人事關係複雜、個個月蝕錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做咗三四個月我都冇癮，我自己走咗；<br />\n因為一來感覺上係有金主好似係為咗贖罪而個個月蝕錢咁，加上嗰排有手足被裁員 (我冇畀人炒，但係有啲冇乜經驗嘅小朋友就&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，我覺得我應該讓返個位出嚟；<br />\n二來我都唔鍾意公司入面啲人事關係同辦公室文化，所以走之前都有同幾位同事嘈過嚟，不過唔講太多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家做緊份濕鳩「文職」，咁腦細的確係黃，但係真係太辛苦<br />\n5.5 days，10中k，<br />\nEmail、電話、WhatsApp、Walk-in客乜撚都要接；<br />\nCS係我，執貨係我，報價係我，跟單又係我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最撚扯火係個仆街腦細當初請我返嚟，仲要冇同我講原來有兩個舊同事一個月內要走，<br />\n結果我5月頭入職，佢之後先請返一兩個返嚟，我就變咗係&quot;年資&quot;最深嗰個員工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁個腦細去撚咗邊？<br />\n我都唔知，我淨係知佢而家日日唔撚返公司，唔知去撚咗邊　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264555c29862baaa27ccc8506572289deb5a6fe3","tid":2101311,"uid":87511,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b5ddfec02b3a43ec4f399e33114745bf2d81fd05","tid":2101311,"uid":353836,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:29:04.000Z","msg":"香港打工叫易上位<br />\n移民咪仲死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:35:03.000Z","msg":"對唔住，我覺得好難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044b155a81b2e119d4243e9e3a1ee88e2d7dbb2e","tid":2101311,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74ed9e1ea1f0564509cdba7df265356199f32830","tid":2101311,"uid":252142,"like":7,"dislike":44,"score":-37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:27:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:35:27.000Z","msg":"25k租屋都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b89ef09b6cb1c5165bbee29a589f7b4875774c","tid":2101311,"uid":87511,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:37:26.000Z","msg":"Btw講起interview，<br />\n諗起請親我嘅腦細/HR事後畀我嘅評價都係以下：<br />\n老實/乖巧/真誠<br />\n<br />\n我覺得其實潛台詞係蠢、戇鳩、豬兜，<br />\n廉價奴工，好洗好用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd00b731d18f36568bfeba46f7d24a818ceeb24","tid":2101311,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"044b155a81b2e119d4243e9e3a1ee88e2d7dbb2e","tid":2101311,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74ed9e1ea1f0564509cdba7df265356199f32830","tid":2101311,"uid":252142,"like":7,"dislike":44,"score":-37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:27:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:35:27.000Z","msg":"25k租屋都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:41:01.000Z","msg":"有狗屋/租金津貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac79491843bd1ca69eae2c15d1f7c28852981e68","tid":2101311,"uid":132585,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:42:05.000Z","msg":"自己香港謀生能力都冇，仲話想去外國生活，屌你老母啦笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8952143c792e0d1276646d766ccf8320c22a353","tid":2101311,"uid":87511,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ac79491843bd1ca69eae2c15d1f7c28852981e68","tid":2101311,"uid":132585,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:42:05.000Z","msg":"自己香港謀生能力都冇，仲話想去外國生活，屌你老母啦笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:44:26.000Z","msg":"有道理<br />\n我而家思考緊一樣嘢<br />\n男人老狗有手有腳學一技之長只要唔怕辛苦，真係唔會餓死<br />\n<br />\n好似我腦細咁廢，純粹有錢開廠做生意，然後唔撚理間公司<br />\n淨係做回頭客都個個月有錢賺"},{"pid":"f0c28e3791f753f884aada636243548968af6b2c","tid":2101311,"uid":87511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:48:23.000Z","msg":"奴工瞓哂? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8984040f60402b2eed261d65909669b55ec53a4","tid":2101311,"uid":69095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0c28e3791f753f884aada636243548968af6b2c","tid":2101311,"uid":87511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:48:23.000Z","msg":"奴工瞓哂? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:50:36.000Z","msg":"某U = 邊間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心態決定境界<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8847b645cf1f82c91d52f1d192da2f7c54b14d54","tid":2101311,"uid":87511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d8984040f60402b2eed261d65909669b55ec53a4","tid":2101311,"uid":69095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0c28e3791f753f884aada636243548968af6b2c","tid":2101311,"uid":87511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:48:23.000Z","msg":"奴工瞓哂? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:50:36.000Z","msg":"某U = 邊間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心態決定境界<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:51:03.000Z","msg":"係三大我就爭住自爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" c